    SPiDApiGetRequest

    Contains a client token request to SPiD using GrantType.CLIENT_CREDENTIALS
    SPiDCodeRequest
    Request a one time authentication code for the current user
    SPiDCodeTokenRequest
    Contains a code access token request to SPiD using GrantType.AUTHORIZATION_CODE
    SPiDFacebookTokenRequest
    Contains a Facebook access token request to SPiD
    SPiDGooglePlusTokenRequest
    Contains a Google+ access token request to SPiD
    SPiDRefreshTokenRequest
    Contains a token refresh request to SPiD
    SPiDRunnableRequest
    Contains a runnable request to SPiD
    SPiDTerms
    Immutable value object for the SPiD terms returned after a successful SPiDTermsRequest
    SPiDTermsRequest
    A request that fetches the SPiD Terms
    SPiDTokenRequest
    Contains a access token request to SPiD
    SPiDUserCredentialTokenRequest
    Contains a user credential access token request to SPiD using GrantType.PASSWORD
    SPiDUserRequest
    A SPiD request that fetches the SPiD user
